soap.local.entity

Class UserContact

  • soap.local.entity.SOAPBaseType
    • soap.local.entity.GWObject
      • soap.local.entity.Contact
        • soap.local.entity.Person
          • soap.local.entity.UserContact

  • public class UserContact
extends Person
    Represents the contact data for a system User as a Person. One UserContact entity will normally exist in the system for each User, and is linked to by a direct foreign key from that User.
